Use on packaging, material handling, printing, manufacturing, gift baskets, and so much more! Makes any project that requires adhesive dots quick and simple. Features an ergonomic, triggerless design that does not require electricity or batteries. Can easily be reloaded and the scrap liner rewinds inside the dispenser.
